    "description": "<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746400/extras/7b056ffb37647ced46f98c19e3a747b9.avif?t=1749651366\" width=600 height=196 /></span><br>以令人惊叹的手绘艺术风格探索腐化的半岛。<br>您将扮演赫伯特·韦斯特马克，一位超自然调查员和古怪小玩意的馆长。与寄生鬼阿姆布罗斯一起，您将探索伯茅斯的地图，以弄清这里的人们为何失踪。您的狂乱之旅将在这独特的宇宙恐怖冒险中何去何从？<br>精美的艺术将为这场高仑恐怖冒险设定基调，赫伯特将通过运用他的技能、物品和卡组来尝试生存。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746400/extras/928452a9b7386850e71e01ba45f88189.poster.avif?t=1749651366\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746400/extras/928452a9b7386850e71e01ba45f88189.webm?t=1749651366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746400/extras/928452a9b7386850e71e01ba45f88189.mp4?t=1749651366\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这款高仑恐怖冒险卡牌构建游戏汲取了H.P.洛夫克拉夫特、斯蒂芬·金和玛丽·雪莱等人的灵感。<br>装备物品和遗物；获得卡牌并在游戏板上使用它们，以在城外最黑暗的角落生存。在舒适的恐怖氛围中对未知进行有趣的探索。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746400/extras/d8a51782189131abda2cd4c0b04273c4.avif?t=1749651366\" width=600 height=196 /></span><br>一款带有全新拼图机制的卡牌游戏，让您在使用手牌之前思考。一个失误可能会让您付出沉重代价。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746400/extras/94342f6c0ca9f4bb823d014ddddd4a44.poster.avif?t=1749651366\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746400/extras/94342f6c0ca9f4bb823d014ddddd4a44.webm?t=1749651366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746400/extras/94342f6c0ca9f4bb823d014ddddd4a44.mp4?t=1749651366\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 探索世界地图上的分支道路，那里藏有随机战利品、相遇和惊喜。<br></li><li> 沉浸在深刻而充满趣味的角色完全配音叙述中。<br></li><li> 分支对话和多个结局。<br></li><li> 个性点数让您升级赫伯特的各种技能。<br></li><li> 技能检查将测试您的角色构建。<br></li><li> 构建您的卡组来抵御伯茅斯市民所受的黑暗腐化之物。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746400/extras/5a79f02c0567dfb06525135ead95cf2c.poster.avif?t=1749651366\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746400/extras/5a79f02c0567dfb06525135ead95cf2c.webm?t=1749651366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746400/extras/5a79f02c0567dfb06525135ead95cf2c.mp4?t=1749651366\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>收集物品以帮助您，并提升您的个性以生存那些追逐您的事物。<br><br>使用您的笔记本与对话选择结合起来，更近距离地了解这里到底发生了什么。<br><br>通过桌游风格的技能检查深入挖掘，看看您还能学到什么——但要注意，失败可能会带来风险。<br><br>在这独特的宇宙恐怖冒险中，您的狂乱之旅将何去何从？",
